{"tid":1784562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環保戰線 中國係拖慢臭氧層修復十年既唯一元凶","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T06:42:47.000Z","uid":165683,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"dd114183406fe41a6170bcb371a1d8f16c9e5684","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"研究員發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">在中國東部一些省份，三氯氟甲烷（CFC-11）的使用量明顯上升</span>。三氯氟甲烷是一種破壞地球臭氧層的氯氟烴物質，這種氣體的排放量上升導致全球臭氧層修復的速度減慢。<br />\n<br />\nBBC環境事務記者馬特&middot;麥格拉思（Matt McGrath）報道，科學家原本預計全球大氣中的三氯氟甲烷含量會逐漸減少，但他們在科學期刊《自然》中刊登的報告指，這個減少的過程從2012年開始變慢，最終排放源頭指向中國。研究員又警告，如果繼續讓中國排放三氯氟甲烷，臭氧層修復的速度<span style=\"color: red;\">可能會被減慢10年。</span><br />\n<br />\nThe data reinforces a watchdog report from 2018 that claimed at least 18 companies in China were using the chemical to make foam insulation.<br />\n<br />\nThe Environmental Investigation Agency, a non-governmental organization that says it investigates &ldquo;environmental crime and abuse,&rdquo; said <span style=\"color: red;\">Chinese executives knew</span> about the use of the banned substance and called enforcement efforts by the<span style=\"color: red;\"> government &ldquo;lax.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://globalnews.ca/news/5306423/china-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F5306423%2Fchina-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d50934c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://globalnews.ca/news/5306423/china-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48377110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48377110&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=8f16f4f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48377110&h=7e562c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48377110</a>"},{"pid":"5cb5616f72f78fa33b284df3383ea938277c0afe","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6249484bc5522f3aeab793f6fddc7738221becb9","tid":1784562,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e5c146611c1d1db9f0fc6301423489a0131d40","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07da9d21809a6bdc1c6d61fb648a665600d3791e","tid":1784562,"uid":50489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e095a17e36d86eff4eb2ba6a7b9eb8b5a5151da7","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d49c3ca42768d7748b81d67379e68e6eaab3dc6","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:03:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"661084cc531a9279e8e7d2d13a06a20a91eb9db1","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:05:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"402e306c6d4a791bb49754e64191975a07537062","tid":1784562,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4f6532b976cef8ca480e8ad48eb83fbe11ca0ac5","tid":1784562,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed75e373dd7fd714f1d1e47734e433ad433f8ff1","tid":17845