的氯氟烴物質，這種氣體的排放量上升導致全球臭氧層修復的速度減慢。<br />\n<br />\nBBC環境事務記者馬特&middot;麥格拉思（Matt McGrath）報道，科學家原本預計全球大氣中的三氯氟甲烷含量會逐漸減少，但他們在科學期刊《自然》中刊登的報告指，這個減少的過程從2012年開始變慢，最終排放源頭指向中國。研究員又警告，如果繼續讓中國排放三氯氟甲烷，臭氧層修復的速度<span style=\"color: red;\">可能會被減慢10年。</span><br />\n<br />\nThe data reinforces a watchdog report from 2018 that claimed at least 18 companies in China were using the chemical to make foam insulation.<br />\n<br />\nThe Environmental Investigation Agency, a non-governmental organization that says it investigates &ldquo;environmental crime and abuse,&rdquo; said <span style=\"color: red;\">Chinese executives knew</span> about the use of the banned substance and called enforcement efforts by the<span style=\"color: red;\"> government &ldquo;lax.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://globalnews.ca/news/5306423/china-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F5306423%2Fchina-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d50934c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://globalnews.ca/news/5306423/china-cfc-11-ozone-chemical-production/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48377110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48377110&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=8f16f4f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48377110&h=7e562c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48377110</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60df202de6bfaf8e713d80e9948f30c81780b97b","tid":1784562,"uid":1656